 185:funsape/peripheral/timer1.hpp ****     //! @brief      Clock prescaler enumeration.
 186:funsape/peripheral/timer1.hpp ****     //! @details    Clock prescaler options associated with TIMER1.
 187:funsape/peripheral/timer1.hpp ****     //! @warning    The value associate with the symbolic names may change
 188:funsape/peripheral/timer1.hpp ****     //!                 between builds and might not reflect the register/bits
 189:funsape/peripheral/timer1.hpp ****     //!                 real values. In order to ensure compatibility between
